# Sankey - KX Dashboards

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/dashboards/sankey/

# Sankey

![Screenshot](../img/sankey/sankey-steps.png)

A Sankey chart is a flow diagram where the width of the flow is proportional
to the rate

## Basics

![Screenshot](../img/sankey/sankeybasics.png)

_Name_

    A name for the component provided by the user. 
_Data Source_

    Has to be a pivot query  [Data sources](../datasources/#pivot-query)
_Focus_

    A [view state parameter](../viewstateparameters/) for [linking](../viewstateparameters/#linking-components) components
_Aggregate Column_

    The dependent [data source](../datasources/) variable used to create the flow map. 
_Show Tooltip_

    Toggle display of tooltip.

